{"nbformat":4,"nbformat_minor":0,"metadata":{"colab":{"provenance":[{"file_id":"1iQpAADS4YOu_DAzhTJpTUfuiQ8D0ghwk","timestamp":1718862187505}],"authorship_tag":"ABX9TyN42Mo2sp8T2EqHKBD1+9rI"},"kernelspec":{"name":"python3","display_name":"Python 3"},"language_info":{"name":"python"}},"cells":[{"cell_type":"markdown","source":["#**BMI CALCULATOR USING PYTHON**\n","\n","Create a command-line BMI calculator in Python. Prompt users for their weight (in kilograms) and height (in meters). Calculate the BMI and classify it into categories (e.g., underweight, normal, overweight) based on predefined ranges. Display the BMI result and category to the user"],"metadata":{"id":"-s7FKfDXNA9X"}},{"cell_type":"code","source":["# Function to calculate BMI\n","def calculate_bmi(weight, height):\n","    bmi = weight / (height ** 2)\n","    return bmi\n","\n","# Get user input\n","try:\n","    weight = float(input(\"Enter your weight in kg: \"))\n","    height = float(input(\"Enter your height in meters: \"))\n","\n","    # Ensure height is not zero to avoid division by zero error\n","    if height <= 0:\n","        raise ValueError(\"Height must be a positive number.\")\n","\n","    # Calculate BMI\n","    bmi = calculate_bmi(weight, height)\n","\n","    # Determine the BMI category\n","    if bmi < 18.5:\n","        category = \"Underweight\"\n","    elif 18.5 <= bmi < 24.9:\n","        category = \"Normal weight\"\n","    elif 25 <= bmi < 29.9:\n","        category = \"Overweight\"\n","    else:\n","        category = \"Obesity\"\n","\n","    # Output the results\n","    print(f\"Your BMI is {bmi:.2f}\")\n","    print(f\"Your BMI category is {category}\")\n","except ValueError as e:\n","    print(f\"Invalid input: {e}\")"],"metadata":{"id":"EMH5JbRGKK84","executionInfo":{"status":"ok","timestamp":1718862137608,"user_tz":-330,"elapsed":34075,"user":{"displayName":"Bhuvana Reddy","userId":"11807274190886738762"}},"outputId":"c15a990c-5f83-447e-bedc-b85c1df53e74","colab":{"base_uri":"https://localhost:8080/"}},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[{"output_type":"stream","name":"stdout","text":["Enter your weight in kg: 26\n","Enter your height in meters: 1.5\n","Your BMI is 11.56\n","Your BMI category is Underweight\n"]}]},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":[],"metadata":{"id":"8v6P_62jM_G7"}}]}